title: iMac A1311 820-2784 don't turn on
message:
I suppose you get light on LED601.
But LED605 MUST too, as you have 3V3_S3.
Please recheck...

ALL_SYS_PWRGD should also be present, with mentioned voltages.
So LED602 must be on too.

title: iMac A1311 820-2784 don't turn on
message: Graphics card can prevent POST. Check if it chimes without graphics card, try another (known good) one if possible.
